ass=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n諗住幫下GAP王手 大家醒水唔好推爆個PO咪無事<br />\n點知比波台自己人反插我一刀 好在走得切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幫喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫倒忙就有"},{"pid":"a65d6ffc372bcef7d25b532d416106ead97e775d","tid":148550,"uid":26115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:11:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>而家好撚多2打6掛住波台個名出去撩事鬥非<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n諗住幫下GAP王手 大家醒水唔好推爆個PO咪無事<br />\n點知比波台自己人反插我一刀 好在走得切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真，岩先想阻止班細蚊仔"},{"pid":"946827de986cd439e3381c3db5c03b5f09a24ffc","tid":148550,"uid":12547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:15:32.000Z","msg":"比2個敗家仔拖累<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fde5bbbf53028b404ab902ec4cefe7d504cc9a02","tid":148550,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:16:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>波台就是波台</blockquote><br />\n縮沙雲"},{"pid":"82f44fad581ec01c3c35bc3f8b08b0388171788a","tid":148550,"uid":47303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:18:06.000Z","msg":"想當年我仲讀緊BAND 3中學<br />\n<br />\n有條MK撚狗咁撚我, 話約我隻揪<br />\n<br />\n佢以為自己有腹肌就好撚好打<br />\n<br />\n(但其實我當時己經舉左兩三年鐵,一直有飲奶粉<br />\n<br />\n不過我BULK緊, 即係夜神起義 Bane 果種大隻型<br />\n<br />\n所以D肌肉線條未現到出黎)<br />\n<br />\n我D 毒撚FD 嚇撚到標尿<br />\n<br />\n「唔好同佢打呀, 佢有腹肌架」<br />\n<br />\n「你痴左線咩, 你見唔見到佢幾咁FIT 呀」<br />\n<br />\n我心諗話你怕你嬲<br />\n<br />\n有腹肌唔等於有力量<br />\n<br />\n我笑笑口咁答應左條MK 放學去籃球場打過<br />\n<br />\nfast forward 去到決戰時間<br />\n<br />\n成班同學企哂係側邊睇<br />\n<br />\n佢就除左件校服<br />\n<br />\n成個小丑咁係到谷佢果幾舊腹肌仔<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到成班以為佢好好打果個情景,我真係快忍不住笑<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然最後佢打到我仆街, 牙都甩埋<br />\n<br />\n但完全同腹肌冇關"},{"pid":"050373871f0c46995ee1198485d22e0dda74c244","tid":148550,"uid":49269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:18:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家好撚多2打6掛住波台個名出去撩事鬥非<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n諗住幫下GAP王手 大家醒水唔好推爆個PO咪無事<br />\n點知比波台自己人反插我一刀 好在走得切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幫喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫倒忙就有</blockquote><br />\n柒左扮醒目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b4f93d804e7dc7769a37d094add9bb9a1e2fc1d","tid":148550,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:19:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一晚出兩隻笠水狗</blockquote><br />\n就快3隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc034252c6bfc9e56d0fc11d5d319624b59d45a9","tid":148550,"uid":2022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:21:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f165076da5c2cbb68ddd3e2e1f09a8c22add5aa","tid":148550,"uid":49269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:23:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一晚出兩隻笠水狗</blockquote><br />\n就快3隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我信中堅賓唔會笠水</blockquote><br />\n牙賓一定唔笠"},{"pid":"6e1fc7390aa7aed0c9a88ddb47e94b252503265a","tid":148550,"uid":1453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:27:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一晚出兩隻笠水狗</blockquote><br />\n就快3隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></bl